 Nick Cave 和 The Bad Seeds 分享“充满活力”的新单曲“Frogs”：“它让我脸上露出了灿烂的笑容” https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-share-exuberant-new-single-frogs-it-just-puts-a-big-fucking-smile-on- my-face-3760636?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-share-exuberant-new-single-frogs-it-just-puts-a-big-fucking-smile-on-my-脸Anagricel DuranWed, 29 May 2024 18:13:38 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3760636 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·凯夫和坏种子。图片来源：梅根·卡伦" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是他们即将发行的第 18 张专辑中的第二首单曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-share-exuberant-new-single-frogs-it-just-puts-a-big-fucking-smile-on-my-face-3760636">Nick Cave 和 The Bad Seeds 分享“充满活力”的新单曲“Frogs”：“它只是让我脸上露出了灿烂的微笑”，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·凯夫和坏种子。图片来源：梅根·卡伦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Nick-Cave-The-Bad-Seeds.-Credit-Megan-Cullen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds">Nick Cave 和 The Bad Seeds</a>分享了他们即将发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds-announce-new-wild-god-album-preorder-3597587">Wild God</a> 》中的“充满活力”的新单曲《Frogs》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/nick-cave-interview-hope-faith-carnage-new-bad-seeds-grinderman-cancel-culture-coronation-3448005"><b>尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）：“没有任何衡量标准表明美德造就优秀的艺术”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌是乐队第 18 张录音室专辑中的第一首歌曲，其中暗指了圣经中该隐和亚伯的故事。 《青蛙》的特色是闪烁的钢琴连复段，贯穿整首歌，凯夫唱着： <em>“迎来了他跪下的一周/用骨头压碎了他兄弟的头/这是我的荣幸/哦宝贝，送你回家，”</em>引用圣经中的第一起谋杀案。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时，凯夫说：“像《Frogs》这样的歌曲充满活力，它让我脸上露出了灿烂的笑容。” 《Frogs》是《Wild God》发行的第二张单曲。该唱片的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds-announce-new-wild-god-album-preorder-3597587">同名歌曲</a>于三月份作为主打单曲发行。 </p><p><iframe title="Nick Cave &amp; The Bad Seeds - Frogs（歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rNfrLoQdB_E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p>定于 8 月 30 日发行的《Wild God》将由 10 首歌曲组成，乐队在传统和实验的主题之间游走——引入左转，增强了主唱创造的丰富意象和情感叙事。您可以<a href="https://nickcave-badseeds.ffm.to/wild-god" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订黑胶唱片</a>。</p><p> “我希望这张专辑对听众的影响就像它对我的影响一样。它从扬声器中爆发出来，我被它所吸引。这是一张复杂的唱片，但它也具有深刻而欢乐的感染力，”凯夫在谈到即将发行的专辑时说道。</p><p> “当我们录制唱片时，从来没有一个总体规划。这些唱片反映了演奏它们的作家和音乐家的情感状态。听着这个，我不知道，看来我们很高兴，”他补充道。 “这张唱片没有任何废话。当它击中时，它就击中了。它会提升你。它让你感动。我喜欢这一点。” </p><figure id="attachment_3597754" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3597754" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3597754" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="《狂野之神》专辑封面" width="2000" height="2007" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-800x803.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-1392x1397.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-1068x1072.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3597754" class="wp-caption-text"> 《狂野之神》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>为了准备专辑的发行，乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-the-making-of-wild-god-part-one-featuring-radioheads-colin-greenwood-3755873">分享了</a>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Radiohead">Radiohead</a>的科林·格林伍德 (Colin Greenwood) 主演的《The Making Of Wild God》的第一部分。</p><p>这段新的独家影片由梅根·卡伦 (Megan Cullen) 执导，在法国 Miraval Studios 录制，让您一睹尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 和 The Bad Seeds 乐队如何创作他们的 LP 的幕后花絮。</p><p>去年，在<em>《信仰、希望与屠杀》</em>一书发行后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/nick-cave-interview-hope-faith-carnage-new-bad-seeds-grinderman-cancel-culture-coronation-3448005">尼克·凯夫接受了<em>《NME》</em>采访，并透露了歌迷对他即将推出的音乐的期待</a>。</p><p>当被问及他是否在音乐中倾注了更多的爱时，他回答说：“我不了解音乐，但这些天我觉得更迫切需要与人联系。</p><p> “这里面有一种责任，也许我以前没有感觉到。我拥有一些非常有价值的东西——制作音乐，我不想浪费这个机会去打电话参加演出或做一些三心二意的尝试。每个人都和彼此一样重要。”</p><p> Cave 最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-add-extra-dates-to-2024-uk-and-european-wild-god-tour-buy-tickets-3618043">宣布了 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演</a>将于今年 9 月在德国拉开帷幕，持续到 10 月，然后在 11 月进行英国巡演。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-tickets/artist/743143?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=W1fRUUS0ZxyPUR9RiQWj01vfUkHWQc1hhRjN2c0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>（英国和爱尔兰）和<a href="https://www.nickcave.com/tour-dates/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（欧洲）购买门票。</p><p>在另一则新闻中，这位音乐家的妻子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/susie-caves-cult-fashion-brand-the-vampires-wife-as-worn-by-florence-welch-and-kylie-minogue-to-shutter-3758604">苏西·凯夫 (Susie Cave) 透露，她的时尚品牌 The Vampires Wife 已关闭</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-share-exuberant-new-single-frogs-it-just-puts-a-big-fucking-smile-on-my-face-3760636">Nick Cave 和 The Bad Seeds 分享“充满活力”的新单曲“Frogs”：“它只是让我脸上露出了灿烂的微笑”，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
